high_descs: Turn left towards the table.
Pick up the left knife on the table.
Turn around and walk towards the black round table.
Place the knife on the purple bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the knife.
Turn around and walk towards the black small table at the corner.
Place the bowl behind the knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a knife on the black table.

high_descs: Move to the table in front of the fridge.
Pick up a knife from the table.
Move to the round  table behind you.
Place the knife in a bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl from the round table.
Move to the end table behind you to the left of the long table in front of the fridge.
Place the bowl on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in bowl on the end table in front of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, then go straight to the table.
Pick up the knife on the table, to the left and near the bread.
Turn left, go to the wall, then turn left and go straight to the table.
Put the knife on the table, in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl on the table, with the knife in it.
Turn around, and walk toward the two tables in front of you.
Place the bow on the leftmost table, to the right of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a knife in it on the table.
